As a UGC creator passionate about skincare, I was thrilled to receive two incredible sunscreens from Dr. Sheth’s – specially formulated for Indian skin!

1. Kesar & Kojic Acid Oil-Free Sunscreen (SPF 50+)
This one’s a powerhouse for those dealing with pigmentation. Infused with Kesar and Kojic Acid, it not only protects from UV, IR, and blue light but also adds a subtle glow to the skin over time. Perfect for oily skin and super lightweight—no white cast, no greasiness.

2. Ceramide & Vitamin C Oil-Free Sunscreen (SPF 50+)
An absolute must-have for bright, healthy skin. The ceramide complex helps strengthen the skin barrier while Vitamin C gives that luminous, even-toned finish. Again, ideal for oily skin types and layers beautifully under makeup.

Overall Thoughts:
Both sunscreens are dermatologist-formulated, water-resistant, and cater to Indian skin needs. I love how they feel on my skin—non-sticky, protective, and effective. These are going straight into my daily routine.
